  "html": "<h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t<span>Scene</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<span>IV</span>\n\t\t\t\t</h3>\n\t\t\t\t<table>\n\t\t\t\t\t<tbody>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td/>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<em><b>Cléante</b>, <b>Damis</b>, <b>Dorine</b>.</em>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Damis</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>I wish you’d say a word to him about</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<br/>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>My sister’s marriage; I suspect Tartuffe</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<br/>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>Opposes it, and puts my father up</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<br/>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>To all these wretched shifts. You know, besides,</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<br/>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>How nearly I’m concerned in it myself;</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<br/>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>If love unites my sister and Valère,</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<br/>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>I love his sister too; and if this marriage</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<br/>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>Were to⁠ ⁠…</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Dorine</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>He’s coming.</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tbody>\n\t\t\t\t</table>\n\t\t\t</section>\n\t\t\t<section id=\"scene-1-5\">"
